<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/32586937-andronikos"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1414257769i/32586937._UX100_CR0,21,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
