<span id="freeTextContainer6376879893280235396">Gene Wolfe, the poetically accented writer of intricate fantasy/science-fiction hybrids like this exquisite tetralogy, was inspired by that other pen-wielding magician Jack Vance&apos;s <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/40866.Tales_of_the_Dying_Earth' rel='nofollow noopener'>
